# Time with Mom Simulator

A Monte Carlo-based simulation tool to model long-term family time under uncertainty.

## Features
- Aging decay modeling
- Stochastic visit frequency
- Multi-phase life modeling (abroad vs domestic)

## Installation

pip install -e .

## Usage

from time_with_mom import simulate

## Demo

streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py
